author: Chuck Todd and Mark Murray  and Carrie Dann
title: First Read: Team Trump Takes Over CPAC
text: Attendees stand for the Pledge of Allegiance during the first day of the Conservative Political Action Conference at the Gaylord National Resort and Convention Center on Feb. 23, 2017 in National Harbor, Maryland. Hosted by the American Conservative Union, CPAC is an annual gathering of right wing politicians, commentators and their supporters.
